<script>
  const userEvents =  ['click', 'keypress'];
  for (let i = 0; i < userEvents.length; i++) {
    let evt = userEvents[i];
    document.querySelector('#icon-section-header').addEventListener(evt, function(e){
      if (document.body.clientWidth < 993) {
        classToggle(e.target);
      }
    });
  }
  function classToggle(elm) {
    elm.classList.toggle('opened');
  }
  let helpDeskBtn = document.querySelector('#helpDeskBtn');
  if (!!helpDeskBtn) {
    let helpDeskLink = 'https://support.nlm.nih.gov/support/create-case?from=' + encodeURIComponent(window.location.href);
    helpDeskBtn.addEventListener('click',  function(){
      window.open(helpDeskLink, '_blank')
    });
  }
  let ncbiHomeBtn = document.querySelector('#ncbiHomeBtn');
  if (!!ncbiHomeBtn) {
    ncbiHomeBtn.addEventListener('click', function(){
      window.open('https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov', '_blank')
    });
  }
  // Following JavaScript is to toggle top banner of page.
  var head_bnr = document.querySelector(".usa-banner header.usa-banner-header");
  var btn_bnr = document.querySelector(".usa-banner button.usa-accordion-button.usa-banner-button");
  var acr_bnr = document.querySelector(".usa-banner div.usa-banner-content.usa-accordion-content");
  btn_bnr.addEventListener("click", function(e) {
    head_bnr.classList.toggle("usa-banner-header-expanded");
    var aria_val = this.getAttribute("aria-expanded");
    var opp_aria_val = (aria_val === "false") ? "true" : "false";
    this.setAttribute("aria-expanded", opp_aria_val);
    acr_bnr.setAttribute("aria-hidden", aria_val);
    e.stopPropagation();
  });
</script>
